data.description: Turnkey, single level home offering 1,807 sq. ft. with 4 bed, 2 bath, new flooring throughout, new paint inside and out, fully remodeled kitchen with new soft close cabinets, quartz stone counters and new appliances. Cozy fireplace in a spacious great room. NO HOA! RV parking. Large lot with room for toys. Tool shed, fenced yard plus an attached 2-car garage. Indoor laundry room. Split floor plan for privacy. Arizona room that is heated and cooled. Gas stub at range. Newer roof. Washer and dryer included. Close to schools, shopping, hospital and restaurants. Low taxes
